        <title>Git Committer Statistics</title>
        <published>2026-03-14T00:00:00+00:00</published>
        <updated>2026-03-14T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
        <author>
            <name>Jason Short</name>
        </author>
        <link rel="alternate" href="https://jashort.github.io/blog/git-committer-statistics/" type="text/html"/>
        <id>https://jashort.github.io/blog/git-committer-statistics/</id>
        
            <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;A few options for getting committer statistics for a git repository:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;print-lines-per-author-with-git-summary-command&quot;&gt;Print lines per author with &lt;code&gt;git summary&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; command&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(from the &lt;a rel=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tj&#x2F;git-extras&#x2F;tree&#x2F;main&quot;&gt;git-extras&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; package: (&lt;code&gt;brew install git-extras&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; on macOS)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-entity z-name z-function&quot;&gt;git&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-string&quot;&gt; summary --line&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellsession&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt;project     :     test&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt;lines       :     1124&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt;authors     :&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt;  1103 Alice        98.1%&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt;    21 Bob           1.9%&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;print-number-of-commits-with-the-git-shortlog-command&quot;&gt;Print number of commits with the &lt;code&gt;git shortlog&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; command:&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellscript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-entity z-name z-function&quot;&gt;git&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-string&quot;&gt; shortlog -s -n -c&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;shellsession&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt; 10  Alice&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-text&quot;&gt;  3  Bob&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;</content>
        <summary type="html">Show committer statistics for a git repository</summary>
